Package: Rthreads
Version: 1.0.2
Author: Norm Matloff <nsmatloff@ucdavis.edu>
Authors@R: person(given = "Norm",
                       family = "Matloff",
                       role = c("aut", "cre"),
                       email = "nsmatloff@ucdavis.edu")
Maintainer: Norm Matloff <nsmatloff@ucdavis.edu>
Date: 2025-05-29
Title: Parallel Threads Environment for R
Description: Provides a threads-type parallel programming environment for R.
   The package gives the R programmer the clearer, more concise
   shared memory world view, and typically gives superior
   performance as well.  
OS_type: unix
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: bigmemory (>= 4.0.0), synchronicity, parallel
LazyLoad: no
License: GPL (>= 2)
